@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F1F8E9
skinparam classBorderColor #33691E
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Rejected : review
Delivered : entry / log classroom
Rejected --> Archived : review
Archived --> Completed : approve
Completed --> Draft : process
Delivered --> Archived : revert
Draft --> [*]
@enduml